Class LettuceFactoryBeanSupport<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.beans.factory.config.AbstractFactoryBean<T>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public abstract class LettuceFactoryBeanSupport<T>
extends org.springframework.beans.factory.config.AbstractFactoryBean<T>
    Adapter for Springs FactoryBean interface to allow easy setup of RedisClient factories via Spring configuration.

    3.0
